snippet.title: NONESSENTIAL (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Your lively and charismatic gamer friend Nathan calls to catch-up.
Talk to Nathan and help him through some of his troubles in this off-beat comedic drama.

This is a game that focuses on mental health and life during the pandemic. 
I hope you enjoy. :D

The game can be played at https://bradkraeling.itch.io/nonessential

Follow me on twitter https://twitter.com/BradKraeling
